      "span_text": "As reported previously, upon stimulation with IL-1α, there was a 5-fold increase in GAG release from explanted porcine articular cartilage, which was not inhibited by TIMP-1 or TIMP-2, but was dose-dependently inhibited by N-TIMP-3."
